1
00:00:04,300 --> 00:00:05,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A wyvern?</font>

2
00:00:05,960 --> 00:00:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like a mage is controlling it.</font>

3
00:00:09,610 --> 00:00:11,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think, Chancellor?</font>

4
00:00:12,220 --> 00:00:15,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wyverns are fundamentally pack animals,</font>

5
00:00:15,250 --> 00:00:18,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so one would never attack
a village on its own.</font>

6
00:00:19,090 --> 00:00:20,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, that mage is present.</font>

7
00:00:21,390 --> 00:00:24,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There could be another threat nearby.</font>

8
00:00:24,280 --> 00:00:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think this is the work
of the Kingdom of Yelenetta?</font>

9
00:00:26,910 --> 00:00:28,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most likely.</font>

10
00:00:28,130 --> 00:00:30,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yelenetta's attacking this village?</font>

11
00:00:30,840 --> 00:00:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Baron, there's a good chance this wyvern
has a small group of elite knights in tow.</font>

12
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:38,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful.</font>

13
00:00:38,010 --> 00:00:39,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

14
00:00:41,010 --> 00:00:45,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although at that altitude,
ballista bolts won't reach it.</font>

15
00:00:46,120 --> 00:00:49,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That leaves one option.
We'll deploy the prototype.</font>

16
00:01:01,370 --> 00:01:06,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EASYGOING TERRITORY DEFENSE
BY THE OPTIMISTIC LORD</font>

17
00:01:06,550 --> 00:01:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 10: A SECRET WEAPON'S
VILLAINOUS ATTACK ON THE HOMELAND</font>

18
00:02:21,510 --> 00:02:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 10: A SECRET WEAPON'S
VILLAINOUS ATTACK ON THE HOMELAND</font>

19
00:02:22,700 --> 00:02:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We'll soon be in enemy territory,
Your Highness.</font>

20
00:02:26,850 --> 00:02:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The wyvern is already scouting
Seatoh from above.</font>

21
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:37,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe they made <i>me</i> lead
the invasion of such a remote village.</font>

22
00:02:38,140 --> 00:02:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Prince Unimog Yelenetta, eighth son
of Yelenetta Kingdom, for pity's sake.</font>

23
00:02:44,570 --> 00:02:50,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The king commanded you to lead
this operation due to its importance.</font>

24
00:02:51,530 --> 00:02:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yelenetta Kingdom has long been rivals
with the neighboring Kingdom of Scuderia.</font>

25
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:04,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, it is now time to settle things
with Scuderia once and for all.</font>

26
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have been entrusted to lead
our glorious vanguard, Prince Unimog.</font>

27
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Conquering a remote village like this
will be a walk in the park.</font>

28
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should be there soon.</font>

29
00:03:21,190 --> 00:03:22,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

30
00:03:22,410 --> 00:03:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What <i>is</i> that?</font>

31
00:03:23,450 --> 00:03:25,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Why is there a fortress city here?</font>

32
00:03:25,900 --> 00:03:29,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did they build something like this
in this remote region?</font>

33
00:03:29,070 --> 00:03:30,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You imbecile!</font>

34
00:03:30,810 --> 00:03:34,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way they could've constructed
a fortress city so easily!</font>

35
00:03:34,690 --> 00:03:39,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They've merely built a facade
that makes it <i>look</i> like a fortress city.</font>

36
00:03:39,340 --> 00:03:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will advance and take their land.</font>

37
00:03:42,420 --> 00:03:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hold on.</font>

38
00:03:43,370 --> 00:03:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

39
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if that fortress <i>is</i> the real deal?</font>

40
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You <i>dare</i> to defy me, you insolent oaf?!</font>

41
00:03:49,380 --> 00:03:51,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm telling you it's all for show.</font>

42
00:03:51,990 --> 00:03:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">F-Forgive me.</font>

43
00:03:54,420 --> 00:03:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, go destroy those ramparts!</font>

44
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've barely made a mark on it.</font>

45
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Impossible. That <i>can't</i> be true.</font>

46
00:04:13,290 --> 00:04:14,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good afternoon!</font>

47
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:18,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Van, the lord of this village.</font>

48
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That <i>child</i>?</font>

49
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What brings you all this way
from the Kingdom of Yelenetta?</font>

50
00:04:26,370 --> 00:04:31,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You imp! How did you know
we're from Yelenetta Kingdom?</font>

51
00:04:31,870 --> 00:04:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So my guess was right.</font>

52
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:37,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just bluffing that I knew,
but you were quick to admit it.</font>

53
00:04:39,310 --> 00:04:42,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This village didn't have ramparts
like this before.</font>

54
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:46,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you turn it into a fortress city?</font>

55
00:04:46,730 --> 00:04:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, the villagers and I worked together
to make the ramparts and facilities.</font>

56
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:54,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">D-Do you take me for a fool?!</font>

57
00:04:54,810 --> 00:04:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get down here now!</font>

58
00:04:56,850 --> 00:05:00,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't expect me to go on easy on you
just because you're a child!</font>

59
00:05:00,350 --> 00:05:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My wyvern can attack you
from the air, you know!</font>

60
00:05:03,490 --> 00:05:05,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your ramparts won't save you!</font>

61
00:05:06,300 --> 00:05:09,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Send a message to the mage
controlling the wyvern.</font>

62
00:05:09,070 --> 00:05:10,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get him to attack them.</font>

63
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:13,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there's a chance
he'll be attacked in return—</font>

64
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:15,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Imbecile!</font>

65
00:05:15,110 --> 00:05:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wyverns are <i>dragons</i>!</font>

66
00:05:16,940 --> 00:05:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way it'd lose!</font>

67
00:05:18,590 --> 00:05:19,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right.</font>

68
00:05:19,710 --> 00:05:23,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, it's time you learned
just how terrifying dragons can be.</font>

69
00:05:25,450 --> 00:05:27,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Panamera. If you would.</font>

70
00:05:27,850 --> 00:05:28,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

71
00:05:30,620 --> 00:05:31,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire!</font>

72
00:05:46,570 --> 00:05:48,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What the...</font>

73
00:05:49,330 --> 00:05:50,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those are shuriken.</font>

74
00:05:51,350 --> 00:05:56,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're thin and light, so I figured
I'd stuff them inside a bomb of sorts.</font>

75
00:05:58,300 --> 00:06:00,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This was your "prototype"?</font>

76
00:06:00,580 --> 00:06:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. That's the first time we've used it,
but it seemed moderately successful.</font>

77
00:06:05,910 --> 00:06:08,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was a ridiculous amount of force.</font>

78
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That could prove to be as much
of a threat as an elemental mage.</font>

79
00:06:12,410 --> 00:06:13,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You.</font>

80
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:16,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the king of Scuderia.</font>

81
00:06:17,450 --> 00:06:21,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What's the king doing
in such a remote village?</font>

82
00:06:22,690 --> 00:06:25,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now then, do you all want to continue?</font>

83
00:06:30,990 --> 00:06:36,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You bunch of cowards!
What are you doing? Protect me!</font>

84
00:06:36,020 --> 00:06:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this? You have plenty
of fight left in you, huh?</font>

85
00:06:39,050 --> 00:06:40,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Panamera?</font>

86
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:47,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next one won't miss!</font>

87
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:46,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Whoa.</font>

88
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The baron is full of surprises.</font>

89
00:06:53,990 --> 00:06:58,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said it. Marquis Fertio
has sired one incredible son.</font>

90
00:06:59,140 --> 00:07:04,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I remember right, I heard the marquis
drove the baron out of his home.</font>

91
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I doubt he ever imagined someone
with a low-ranking magical aptitude</font>

92
00:07:10,220 --> 00:07:12,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would be capable of such feats.</font>

93
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When we return to the capital,</font>

94
00:07:14,980 --> 00:07:18,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'll have to reconsider
our research into magical aptitudes.</font>

95
00:07:23,530 --> 00:07:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now then, Your Highness.
Might you tell us what your strategy was?</font>

96
00:07:29,290 --> 00:07:31,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way I'm telling you.</font>

97
00:07:32,020 --> 00:07:34,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that <i>is</i> unfortunate.</font>

98
00:07:34,340 --> 00:07:36,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Viscountess Cayenne?</font>

99
00:07:37,710 --> 00:07:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I rip out your fingernails
one at a time or gouge out your eyes?</font>

100
00:07:43,030 --> 00:07:44,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which would you prefer?</font>

101
00:07:46,100 --> 00:07:49,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't! Okay! I'll talk! I'll talk!</font>

102
00:07:51,350 --> 00:07:57,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yelenetta Kingdom has been planning
this invasion for several years now.</font>

103
00:07:57,780 --> 00:07:59,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

104
00:07:59,710 --> 00:08:05,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We start by conquering this village
in Marquis Fertio's lands.</font>

105
00:08:05,850 --> 00:08:09,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We assumed taking control of
this remote village would be easy.</font>

106
00:08:11,820 --> 00:08:15,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet you were bested here.
How embarrassing.</font>

107
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:19,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you planning to invade
other territories as well?</font>

108
00:08:20,050 --> 00:08:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At this very moment, a separate force
is attacking the city we're truly after.</font>

109
00:08:25,130 --> 00:08:27,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which one would that be?</font>

110
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:31,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fortress city of Scudet.</font>

111
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:38,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My threats got the information out of him.</font>

112
00:08:38,860 --> 00:08:42,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So Scudet is their target?</font>

113
00:08:42,210 --> 00:08:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe Your Majesty and I should
hasten back to the royal capital.</font>

114
00:08:46,470 --> 00:08:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should marshal our knights at once
and ride to the defense of Scudet.</font>

115
00:08:52,090 --> 00:08:57,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm broadly in agreement.
But allow me to add one request.</font>

116
00:08:57,410 --> 00:08:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

117
00:08:59,100 --> 00:09:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Baron Van Nei Fertio.</font>

118
00:09:01,330 --> 00:09:05,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I request you join us
in our defense of Scudet.</font>

119
00:09:05,860 --> 00:09:06,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

120
00:09:06,950 --> 00:09:09,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're against the idea, boy?</font>

121
00:09:12,890 --> 00:09:16,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Normally, I wouldn't be able to say no
in this situation, but I won't yield.</i></font>

122
00:09:17,170 --> 00:09:20,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Because I want to hole up in this village.</i></font>

123
00:09:21,370 --> 00:09:23,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am greatly honored by your request,</font>

124
00:09:23,940 --> 00:09:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but leaving this village while it's still
developing is akin to abandoning it.</font>

125
00:09:29,130 --> 00:09:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though it possesses weapons
capable of firing holes in wyverns</font>

126
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:37,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and defenses that can fell
armored lizards and dragons,</font>

127
00:09:37,450 --> 00:09:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you claim it is still "developing"?</font>

128
00:09:39,900 --> 00:09:44,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I've barely completed
a tenth of what I envision.</font>

129
00:09:44,660 --> 00:09:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's much more
I'd like to make for it.</font>

130
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:54,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are amusing, boy.</font>

131
00:09:54,930 --> 00:09:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait to see what you make that's
even <i>more</i> incredible than all of that.</font>

132
00:09:59,470 --> 00:10:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However...</font>

133
00:10:00,530 --> 00:10:03,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should accept this request.</font>

134
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every noble must come to
the nation's aid when it's in danger.</font>

135
00:10:08,290 --> 00:10:12,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's essentially the covenant you forge
when you become a noble.</font>

136
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:16,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

137
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it's a noble's duty, I'll participate.</font>

138
00:10:19,930 --> 00:10:23,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, I still have
my responsibilities as a lord.</font>

139
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please allow me to organize
my troops myself.</font>

140
00:10:27,910 --> 00:10:29,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You may do as you wish.</font>

141
00:10:31,880 --> 00:10:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I finally got the village's
defenses all set up,</font>

142
00:10:35,260 --> 00:10:38,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and now I'm being told to leave
the village and go fight.</font>

143
00:10:39,470 --> 00:10:44,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At any rate, can I ask you to protect
this village as its acting lord, Esparda?</font>

144
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, but will you
be all right without me?</font>

145
00:10:49,450 --> 00:10:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I am a bit anxious about that,</font>

146
00:10:52,090 --> 00:10:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but only someone with your ability
can serve as lord in my stead.</font>

147
00:10:56,630 --> 00:10:57,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand.</font>

148
00:10:58,830 --> 00:11:02,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dee, you and the Seatoh Chivalric Order
will come with me, right?</font>

149
00:11:02,790 --> 00:11:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

150
00:11:04,110 --> 00:11:06,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Till and Khamsin, it'll be dangerous, so—</font>

151
00:11:06,050 --> 00:11:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm coming, too!
I'm coming with you, okay?</font>

152
00:11:08,650 --> 00:11:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm coming, too.</font>

153
00:11:10,290 --> 00:11:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. Understood.</font>

154
00:11:14,100 --> 00:11:17,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But will this be enough?</font>

155
00:11:17,250 --> 00:11:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People in the royal capital won't claim I
showed up with too few troops, will they?</font>

156
00:11:22,850 --> 00:11:28,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This will be more than enough
to those who know your might,</font>

157
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:30,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but to those who don't? Hard to say.</font>

158
00:11:30,430 --> 00:11:31,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

159
00:11:32,220 --> 00:11:35,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you mind if we accept
a quest to guard you?</font>

160
00:11:35,180 --> 00:11:36,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? You'd do that?</font>

161
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:39,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Normally, we'd have nothing
to do with any wars.</font>

162
00:11:39,900 --> 00:11:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we don't mind accepting
a quest to guard you.</font>

163
00:11:43,430 --> 00:11:45,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, I'm glad to hear it!</font>

164
00:11:45,530 --> 00:11:48,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, could you reach out
to the other adventurers, too?</font>

165
00:11:48,990 --> 00:11:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell them I'll pay one large gold
and five gold per person.</font>

166
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll give us that much?</font>

167
00:11:55,060 --> 00:11:57,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're risking your lives, after all.</font>

168
00:11:57,140 --> 00:12:01,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for this.
I'm sure everyone will gladly accept.</font>

169
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:04,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're coming with us, right, Kusala?</font>

170
00:12:04,300 --> 00:12:06,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're forcing me to do stuff <i>again</i>?</font>

171
00:12:06,740 --> 00:12:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be honest, it's because I don't
have a suitable scout among my knights.</font>

172
00:12:12,130 --> 00:12:14,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that's true.</font>

173
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if it's a quest, I'd at least like
to be <i>asked</i> whether I'll accept it or not.</font>

174
00:12:20,460 --> 00:12:26,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? But if you don't accept the quest,
you can't come to the barbecue.</font>

175
00:12:26,180 --> 00:12:28,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! I'd miss out on the barbecue?!</font>

176
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, sure, I'm coming! Of course I am!</font>

177
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:33,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy.</font>

178
00:12:36,180 --> 00:12:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm returning to Count Ferdinatto
to report all of this,</font>

179
00:12:39,940 --> 00:12:43,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but after, I'll round up my troops
and head for Scudet at once.</font>

180
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, we might see each other there.</font>

181
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What weapons are you taking?</font>

182
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:52,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to take some
of my creations with me,</font>

183
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:55,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I can't bring any ballistae
as they are right now.</font>

184
00:12:55,770 --> 00:12:56,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case...</font>

185
00:12:57,580 --> 00:13:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll bring my marionette.</font>

186
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your marionette?</font>

187
00:13:01,510 --> 00:13:02,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, you mean...</font>

188
00:13:06,940 --> 00:13:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This will be the Seatoh
Chivalric Order's first campaign.</font>

189
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:15,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our mission is to defend our largest
neighbor, the fortress city of Scudet.</font>

190
00:13:15,060 --> 00:13:17,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our foes are knights from
the Kingdom of Yelenetta.</font>

191
00:13:17,930 --> 00:13:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They've tested our nation's borders
countless times,</font>

192
00:13:20,850 --> 00:13:23,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and unlike us,
they'll be very experienced.</font>

193
00:13:23,690 --> 00:13:26,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, there's nothing to fear.</font>

194
00:13:26,010 --> 00:13:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We won't be going to the front lines.</font>

195
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:30,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What does he mean?</font>

196
00:13:30,980 --> 00:13:32,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}So how do we defeat the enemy?</font>

197
00:13:32,350 --> 00:13:39,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because our goal is for everyone here
to return to this village, safe and sound.</font>

198
00:13:39,570 --> 00:13:43,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As your lord, I'm responsible for
the lives you're entrusting me with.</font>

199
00:13:44,290 --> 00:13:47,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do everything in my power
to protect all of you.</font>

200
00:13:47,660 --> 00:13:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So cherish your own lives as well.</font>

201
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:56,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, once we're done with this battle,
let's develop this village together...</font>

202
00:13:57,870 --> 00:14:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and enjoy another barbecue!</font>

203
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}MARQUIS JALPA BUL ATI FERTIO</font>

204
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Scudet's been attacked?</font>

205
00:14:04,230 --> 00:14:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yes. The Kingdom of Yelenetta
has dispatched soldiers.</font>

206
00:14:10,130 --> 00:14:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Scudet's impregnable.
It won't fall that easily.</font>

207
00:14:15,150 --> 00:14:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll marshal the troops
and ride out immediately.</font>

208
00:14:18,140 --> 00:14:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

209
00:14:19,060 --> 00:14:22,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Send emissaries to the neighboring lords
to request troops from them as well.</font>

210
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:29,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The village governed by your son,
Lord Van, is near Scudet, so should we—</font>

211
00:14:29,330 --> 00:14:32,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That village won't have
any troops to dispatch.</font>

212
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:36,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They can barely earn enough to eat.</font>

213
00:14:36,780 --> 00:14:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, according to the merchants
who came to the royal capital,</font>

214
00:14:40,850 --> 00:14:44,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Van has earned the title
of baron for defeating a dragon.</font>

215
00:14:43,450 --> 00:14:44,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Drivel.</font>

216
00:14:44,640 --> 00:14:49,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Van doesn't possess elemental magic.
There's no way he could defeat a dragon.</font>

217
00:14:49,970 --> 00:14:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That may be true,
but Lord Van isn't a normal child.</font>

218
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:57,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He might have done
something extraordinary—</font>

219
00:14:57,330 --> 00:14:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just hurry up with the preparations.</font>

220
00:14:59,860 --> 00:15:01,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're heading to Scudet at once.</font>

221
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:02,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

222
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FORTRESS CITY OF SCUDET, SOUTH GATE</font>

223
00:15:07,740 --> 00:15:11,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impossible. Scudet's impregnable
ramparts have been...</font>

224
00:15:13,010 --> 00:15:17,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn that Yelenetta,
employing so many wyvern squads...</font>

225
00:15:18,370 --> 00:15:20,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're withdrawing to regroup!</font>

226
00:15:20,330 --> 00:15:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

227
00:15:21,780 --> 00:15:24,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scuderia's reinforcements are here!</font>

228
00:15:24,380 --> 00:15:26,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take this!</font>

229
00:15:27,570 --> 00:15:29,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that weapon?</font>

230
00:15:32,180 --> 00:15:35,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Jalpa! Our forces
have nearly been wiped out!</font>

231
00:15:35,090 --> 00:15:36,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?</font>

232
00:15:41,100 --> 00:15:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this the end?</font>

233
00:15:44,590 --> 00:15:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're leaving without finishing us off?</font>

234
00:15:46,890 --> 00:15:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What in the world is going on?</font>

235
00:15:51,280 --> 00:15:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FORTRESS CITY SCUDET'S WEST GATE</font>

236
00:16:05,630 --> 00:16:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What <i>is</i> that thing?</font>

237
00:16:08,460 --> 00:16:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up and summon
all of our wyverns here!</font>

238
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir! At once!</font>

239
00:16:13,290 --> 00:16:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Automaton: Uno!</font>

240
00:16:19,210 --> 00:16:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it.</font>

241
00:16:20,410 --> 00:16:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up and crush that thing!</font>

242
00:16:26,250 --> 00:16:29,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arte, you're incredible!
I can't believe you can do that!</font>

243
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:34,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who would've believed Scudet
could get conquered so easily?</font>

244
00:16:34,250 --> 00:16:38,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They must have used those wyverns
and that new weapon.</font>

245
00:16:38,160 --> 00:16:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems the damage on
the south gate side is huge.</font>

246
00:16:41,270 --> 00:16:44,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scuderia's knights should be
responding over there.</font>

247
00:16:44,740 --> 00:16:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although they'll probably be forced
to retreat with Scudet in this state.</font>

248
00:16:51,310 --> 00:16:52,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't want to overdo it,</i></font>

249
00:16:52,900 --> 00:16:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but if we draw the enemies to us,
that'll provide some support, right?</i></font>

250
00:16:57,330 --> 00:17:01,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Let's keep this up
and buy the knights some time to retreat.</font>

251
00:17:01,340 --> 00:17:02,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

252
00:17:02,310 --> 00:17:04,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There they are! Over here!</font>

253
00:17:07,310 --> 00:17:09,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll protect you, Lady Arte!</font>

254
00:17:09,990 --> 00:17:11,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm firing!</font>

255
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going to fight, too!</font>

256
00:17:16,040 --> 00:17:17,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

257
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:19,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aim for that group!</font>

258
00:17:19,620 --> 00:17:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoopsie. Can't let you go doing that.</font>

259
00:17:23,510 --> 00:17:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, but we can't afford to lose.</font>

260
00:17:27,150 --> 00:17:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel bad for you.</font>

261
00:17:31,710 --> 00:17:33,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good work, everyone.</font>

262
00:17:40,290 --> 00:17:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Arte.</font>

263
00:17:41,950 --> 00:17:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it.</font>

264
00:17:43,100 --> 00:17:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Crush them with all of our forces!</font>

265
00:17:48,900 --> 00:17:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, we lured a lot to us.</font>

266
00:17:51,230 --> 00:17:54,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I think we've bought them
enough time to escape.</font>

267
00:17:54,970 --> 00:17:57,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, it's time to pull back.</font>

268
00:17:57,880 --> 00:18:02,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we really running away?
We might actually win this, you know.</font>

269
00:18:02,100 --> 00:18:04,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember what I said at the start?</font>

270
00:18:04,300 --> 00:18:08,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our number one goal is for everyone
to make it home in one piece.</font>

271
00:18:09,630 --> 00:18:14,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anyone dies, I won't be happy
at all, even if we do win.</font>

272
00:18:14,360 --> 00:18:17,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or does anyone here have a death wish?</font>

273
00:18:19,950 --> 00:18:23,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, let's all run away
as fast as we can.</font>

274
00:18:23,120 --> 00:18:24,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

275
00:18:27,260 --> 00:18:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Jalpa, what's our next move?</font>

276
00:18:31,330 --> 00:18:34,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We must retake Scudet.</font>

277
00:18:34,930 --> 00:18:38,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll reorganize our knights.
Make the arrangements at once.</font>

278
00:18:38,490 --> 00:18:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

279
00:18:40,660 --> 00:18:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still...</font>

280
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:45,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm surprised we made it back alive.</font>

281
00:18:46,750 --> 00:18:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What in the world happened?</font>

282
00:18:48,330 --> 00:18:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father.</font>

283
00:18:50,700 --> 00:18:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Murcia? You're late. Where were you?</font>

284
00:18:54,270 --> 00:18:55,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My apologies.</font>

285
00:18:57,350 --> 00:19:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marquis Jalpa Bul Ati Fertio.</font>

286
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're making the youngster
cower, you realize.</font>

287
00:19:04,700 --> 00:19:07,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty, I apologize
for that unseemly display.</font>

288
00:19:07,620 --> 00:19:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marquis, you may rise.</font>

289
00:19:10,020 --> 00:19:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the situation in Scudet?</font>

290
00:19:13,620 --> 00:19:16,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scudet has fallen.</font>

291
00:19:16,450 --> 00:19:18,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fallen, you say?!</font>

292
00:19:19,940 --> 00:19:25,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our knights were attacked by
their new weapon and nearly wiped out.</font>

293
00:19:26,100 --> 00:19:28,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you manage to get away?</font>

294
00:19:28,430 --> 00:19:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, for some reason, their wyverns
suddenly stopped pursuing us</font>

295
00:19:32,460 --> 00:19:34,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and headed for the west gate.</font>

296
00:19:34,890 --> 00:19:38,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were most likely drawn there
by Baron Van's reinforcements.</font>

297
00:19:38,940 --> 00:19:39,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

298
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:41,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">V-Van?</font>

299
00:19:41,970 --> 00:19:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose we haven't sent word
to your march yet.</font>

300
00:19:45,830 --> 00:19:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Baron Van has developed that
remote village and defeated a dragon,</font>

301
00:19:50,620 --> 00:19:53,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">earning himself a title at a tender age.</font>

302
00:19:54,660 --> 00:20:00,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Van isn't an elemental mage.
There's no way he could have—</font>

303
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marquis, are you suggesting we're lying?</font>

304
00:20:05,270 --> 00:20:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No, I would never.</font>

305
00:20:08,350 --> 00:20:11,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So Van has earned a title?</i></font>

306
00:20:11,560 --> 00:20:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Young man, are you frustrated your
younger brother earned glory before you?</font>

307
00:20:16,570 --> 00:20:18,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The opposite.</font>

308
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:21,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm very proud of him.</font>

309
00:20:25,580 --> 00:20:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, that certainly wore me out.</font>

310
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Van, what are you
planning to do next?</font>

311
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:36,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure.</font>

312
00:20:36,490 --> 00:20:39,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I've fulfilled my duty as a noble,</font>

313
00:20:39,750 --> 00:20:44,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if Scudet isn't retaken, it means
leaving a threat nearby long-term.</font>

314
00:20:45,340 --> 00:20:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Van. This was my first time
actually witnessing war,</font>

315
00:20:49,710 --> 00:20:54,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but to me, it felt like a terrifying place
where even innocent people are sacrificed.</font>

316
00:20:55,490 --> 00:20:58,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to go there again
if I can avoid it.</font>

317
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:05,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, we're allied with Lady Panamera
who's involved in this war,</font>

318
00:21:05,540 --> 00:21:08,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I think we'll have to provide
some form of aid.</font>

319
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

320
00:21:15,080 --> 00:21:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's develop a new weapon.
Next is the catapult.</font>

321
00:21:18,710 --> 00:21:23,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Deliver some to the battlefield, and we
can claim we provided plenty of support.</font>

322
00:21:32,230 --> 00:21:34,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's rather big, isn't it?</font>

323
00:21:34,260 --> 00:21:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many are you planning to make?</font>

324
00:21:37,020 --> 00:21:40,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think twenty stationary ones
and five mobile ones should suffice.</font>

325
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:46,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but I guess it'd be difficult
to transport that many to Scudet.</font>

326
00:21:47,180 --> 00:21:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The roads there <i>were</i>
in pretty bad condition.</font>

327
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. I can just make them on-site.</font>

328
00:21:56,380 --> 00:21:59,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. That's an option, too.</font>

329
00:21:59,810 --> 00:22:04,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let's start our strategy meeting
in preparation for tomorrow!</font>

330
00:22:15,980 --> 00:22:20,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: JOHN PICKETT</font>

331
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:24,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TIMING: ANDY ELLIS
EDITING: SMR</font>

332
00:22:24,950 --> 00:22:29,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}QUALITY CONTROL: RILEY DALTON
TRANSLATION CHECK: REI MIYASAKA</font>

333
00:23:35,010 --> 00:23:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}NEXT EPISODE: THE ULTIMATE SQUAD'S
PROUD COUNTERATTACK</font>

